author: Libby Cathey, Erin Schumaker
title: Timeline: When Americans can return to work
description: While a battle brews between federal and state powers, Americans are left questioning when life will get back to normal -- and when will everyone return to work?
content:
Americans are in the midst of battling the COVID-19 pandemic, but a key question on many politicians' and residents' minds is when the economy is going to open up again.
